name: Aether Pro 70 Pack - Men's
description: If you speak the language of Type II fun—alpine climbs with remote basecamps, or ambitious thru-hikes where the only trail is the one you make—the Osprey Aether Pro 70 pack is for you.
brand.name: Osprey

name: Soelden Pro 32 Avalanche Airbag Pack - Men's
description: Professional guides, athletes and backcountry recreationalists helped design the lightweight Osprey Soelden Pro 30 avalanche pack for men to make grinding up the skin track as painless as possible.
brand.name: Osprey

name: JetForce Tour 26 Avalanche Airbag Pack
description: Head out into the backcountry prepared for an avalanche with the Black Diamond JetForce Tour 26 pack, featuring the electronic Alpride E1 airbag system powered by cutting-edge supercapacitors.
brand.name: Black Diamond

name: Aether Plus 100 Pack - Men's
description: Whether you're tackling a summit or headed out on a cushy weekend trip filled with creature comforts, the Osprey Aether Plus 100 pack is a large-volume workhorse for your grandest adventures.
brand.name: Osprey

name: Manta 34 Hydration Pack - Men's
description: Trek the path less traveled with all of your essentials on hand. The men's Osprey Manta 34 hydration pack helps you carry your gear and keep the H2O flowing while you get your boots dirty.
brand.name: Osprey

name: Router Pack
description: With space for a large laptop and a weekend's worth of gear, The North Face Router pack is your quintessential get-out-of-town bag for work trips—or camping trips.
brand.name: The North Face

name: Skarab 30 Hydration Pack - Men's
description: When you're in it for the summit, having a versatile and comfortable hiking pack is key. The men's Osprey Skarab 30 hydration pack has the storage and practical touches for all-day hikes.
brand.name: Osprey

name: Powderhound 12 Hydration Pack
description: With 12 liters of storage space and a 3-liter reservoir, the CamelBak Powderhound 12 hydration pack has you covered for quick backcountry missions and all-day lift laps.
brand.name: CamelBak

description: Keep the H2O flowing on steep scrambles and quad-burning switchbacks with the women's Osprey Mira 32 hydration pack. This adjustable, ventilated pack offers dialed-in comfort on the toughest of treks.
brand.name: Osprey

name: Hydraulics Reservoir - 3 Liters
description: The 3-liter Osprey Hydraulics reservoir is ideal for large-volume packs and long-duration activities.
brand.name: Osprey
